rich,

  you've posed an interesting problem.  we have the current un*x
  implementation of the static host tables and currently use your
  proposal of ordering the desired hosts by hand.  we've moved several
  hosts, including the NIC, up into our local section of the host
  table.  however, this has the disadvantage of becoming out of date
  should the nic or whoever else we have yanked into the local section
  change their address.

  i'd like to see this routing done automatically.

							--bw

